OL,7,FAn investigation into a rollercoaster
OL,8,Fderailment at Coney Beach Amusement
OL,9,FPark in Porthcawl found safety issues
OL,10,Fon a second ride.
OL,12,FInspectors launched an investigation
OL,13,Fafter a rollercoaster called the Wacky
OL,14,FWorm derailed on 13 August, with 13
OL,15,Fchildren and one adult sustaining
OL,16,Fminor injuries and some requiring
OL,17,Fhospital treatment.
