OL,7,FThe Health and Safety Executive said
OL,8,Fin an update that the ride - which
OL,9,FConey Beach said was a third-party
OL,10,Fride not owned by the funfair - is now
OL,11,Fbeing inspected at its laboratory in
OL,12,FBuxton, Derbyshire.
OL,14,FA HSE statement said: "Other rides at
OL,15,Fthe park were inspected and one nearby
OL,16,Fride, the Mini Jet Ride, was also
OL,17,Fissued with a prohibition notice, but
OL,18,Fhas been subsequently repaired after
OL,19,Fsafety issues were found."
