OL,7,FA spokesperson for Coney Beach's
OL,8,Fowners said: "During HSE
OL,9,Finvestigations into the unfortunate
OL,10,Faccident on the Wacky Worm ride, a
OL,11,Fminor and completely unrelated issue
OL,12,Fwas identified with the external
OL,13,Fwalkway adjacent to the nearby Mini
OL,14,FJet ride which required the
OL,15,Finstallation of some wooden packing of
OL,16,Fabout 6mm to ensure it did not vibrate
OL,17,For feel insecure underfoot.
