OL,7,F"It had absolutely no relevance to the
OL,8,Fintegrity of the ride itself. The
OL,9,Frepair took no more than 10 minutes
OL,10,Fduring which the ride was closed.
OL,11,FPermission was then given for it to
OL,12,Foperate as normal for the remainder of
OL,13,Fthe day.
OL,15,F"The ride was owned and operated by a
OL,16,Fthird-party business which has
OL,17,Fsubsequently sold it and removed in
OL,18,Ffrom the park as part of our winding
OL,19,Fdown and closure by the end of October
OL,20,Ffollowing acquisition of the site by
OL,21,Fthe Welsh Government for redevelopment.
