OL,3,CInspectors found safety issue on
OL,4,Csecond ride at funfair during
OL,5,Cinspection
OL,7,FSimon Chilcott, principal inspector at
OL,8,FHSE, said: "While the school summer
OL,9,Fholidays are now over, it is
OL,10,Fcompletely understandable that many
OL,11,Fpeople continue to feel the impact of
OL,12,Fwhat happened in Porthcawl last month.
OL,14,F"We've worked very closely with the
OL,15,Fpolice and taken swift action to
OL,16,Fpreserve evidence and keep people
OL,17,Fsafe. Witness accounts have been
OL,18,Fshared with us, as well as footage
OL,19,Ftaken on the day of the incident, and
OL,20,Fthese will be used to inform our
OL,21,Finvestigation.
